REPH Acquisition Co said its boardappointed a special committee to negotiate the terms of anoffer made earlier today by &lt;Pesch and Co> to merge with itsRepublic Health Corp &lt;REPH> unit.    Pesch, through its Alpha Health Systems Corp unit, offeredto acquire the 36 pct of Republic Health stock that it does notalready own.    Terms of Pesch's offer have not been disclosed.    Reuter&#3;